{"tid":2421400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁子超：K11食肆爆疫反映「安心出行」對遏止群組爆發沒有任何幫助","createTime":"2021-02-24T13:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T14:27:35.000Z","uid":5195,"like":157,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"636ec88f18e671837a72fbad49075829295afd90","tid":2421400,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"呼吸系統科專科醫生梁子超認為，事件反映了要求食客使用「安心出行」應用程式，對遏止群組爆發沒有任何幫助，只能事後追蹤；但病毒可以在環境存活一段長時間，很可能已經擴散開去。他強調，政府不應以「安心出行」二維碼或強制紀錄食客行蹤，用作放寬社交距離措施的條件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210224/DLZW7B7RHNHCPCFN66RI2HJVH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210224%2FDLZW7B7RHNHCPCFN66RI2HJVH4%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8IICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=7bded5e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210224%2FDLZW7B7RHNHCPCFN66RI2HJVH4%2F&h=99b6e035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210224/DLZW7B7RHNHCPCFN66RI2HJVH4/</a>"},{"pid":"a418cdfcfa0c413672f6507131ca331e89ecd7ad","tid":2421400,"uid":10905,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"梁子超一開頭都企中間彈出彈入<br />\n而加直頭變左大隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e54f69d70b7386504cac6d6430004d01a78ee5","tid":2421400,"uid":107681,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"a418cdfcfa0c413672f6507131ca331e89ecd7ad","tid":2421400,"uid":10905,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"梁子超一開頭都企中間彈出彈入<br />\n而加直頭變左大隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"視國安法如無物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de